Neil Brown Jr. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neil_Brown_Jr. 0 Cornelius C. Brown Jr. (born June 19, 1980), better known as Neil Brown Jr., is an American actor. His most recognizable role may be in the television series The Walking Dead as Guillermo, leader of the Vatos and as Felix on the short-lived South Beach on the former UPN. He also played DJ Yella in the 2015 biopic, Straight Outta Compton. Cornelius_C._Brown_Jr. ( born June_19_,_1980 ) , better_known as Neil_Brown_Jr. , is an_American_actor .
